.. parsonsprob:: aaa
   :author: Matthew Zuniga
   :difficulty: 0.0
   :basecourse: fopp
   :topic: GeneralIntro/Exercises
   :from_source: F
   :language: c++

   Construct a block of code that correctly implements the accumulator pattern.
   -----
   template < class InputIt, class T >
   T sum(InputIt first, InputIt last, T value)
   {
       while (first != last) {
          value = value + *first;
          ++first;
       }
       return value;
   }